530
00:31:18,480 --> 00:31:20,040
Hamba pantas mati.

531
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:35,800
Lapor Baginda,

532
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:36,680
Adipati Chu.

533
00:31:37,160 --> 00:31:38,560
Nona Cheng memang benar

534
00:31:38,560 --> 00:31:39,800
