549
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:27,000
Tetua Shen,

550
00:32:27,800 --> 00:32:28,800
karena kau sudah datang,

551
00:32:29,200 --> 00:32:30,320
aku jadi tidak khawatir lagi.

552
00:32:31,480 --> 00:32:32,520
Mohon Anda periksa

