556
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,760
Hukuman peremukan tulang.

557
00:33:39,480 --> 00:33:40,280
Nona,

558
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:42,840
minumlah obat ini.

559
00:33:48,160 --> 00:33:48,880
Air.

560
00:33:50,480 --> 00:33:50,960
Ayo,

561
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:51,640
Nona,

562
00:33:52,000 --> 00:33:52,760
