590
00:36:27,560 --> 00:36:29,320
sangat aktif, nadinya seperti
mutiara berputar.

591
00:36:29,480 --> 00:36:31,080
Memang benar denyut nadi
orang yang mengandung.

592
00:36:32,040 --> 00:36:32,880
Tetua Shen,

593
00:36:33,160 --> 00:36:34,360
kenapa kau juga…

594
00:36:39,760 --> 00:36:41,400
Jangan-jangan Yu'er sungguh-sungguh…

595
00:36:42,880 --> 00:36:44,320
Jika mereka benar-benar
sampai ke tahap ini

596
00:36:44,680 --> 00:36:45,680
juga bagus.

597
00:36:46,440 --> 00:36:47,840
Tapi malah di saat ini.

598
00:36:48,080 --> 00:36:48,800
Tapi,

599
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:50,280
denyut nadi ini

600
00:36:50,600 --> 00:36:51,640
harusnya muncul

601
00:36:51,640 --> 00:36:53,320
ketika sudah mengandung

602
00:36:53,400 --> 00:36:55,000
selama empat bulan.

603
00:36:56,200 --> 00:36:58,120
Bulan kelima hari ketujuh,

604
00:36:58,880 --> 00:37:00,120
