628
00:38:00,720 --> 00:38:03,440
Kalau begitu aku bisa tenang saja.

629
00:38:13,480 --> 00:38:14,360
Pengurus Bidak.

630
00:38:30,560 --> 00:38:31,240
Ayah.

631
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:33,640
Letakkan saja.

632
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:39,680
Izinkan aku pergi ganti baju sebentar.

633
